{"id":"hashub","term":"Hashub","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Intelligent. (1.) A Levite of the family of Merari (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Nehemiah 11:15\">Neh. 11:15</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 9:14\">1 Chr. 9:14</a>). (2.) <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Nehemiah 3:23\">Neh. 3:23</a>. 3:11.</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Nehemiah 11:15","1 Chronicles 9:14","Nehemiah 3:23"]}